title: My Indigo - Auerspergstrasse
typeOfFood: Chinese, Japanese, Thai, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Asian fusion restaurant chain offering mixed cuisines with mainly curries, stir-fries, and sushi. A variety of ready-made meals to choose from as well as a salad bar. Various juices and drinks.
